[{"location":"#ForecastVerification","page":"ForecastVerification","title":"ForecastVerification","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"ForecastVerification","title":"ForecastVerification","text":"ForecastVerification Julia package repo.","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"ForecastVerification","title":"ForecastVerification","text":"Modules = [ForecastVerification]","category":"page"},{"location":"#ForecastVerification.CRPS-Tuple{AbstractArray{T,2} where T,AbstractArray{T,1} where T}","page":"ForecastVerification","title":"ForecastVerification.CRPS","text":"crps = CRPS(X::AbstractMatrix,xobs::AbstractVector)\n\nThe Continuous Rank Probability Score (CRPS) from an ensemble X (cases,members) using the observation xobs (cases). The CRPS is averaged over all cases.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#ForecastVerification.brierscore-Tuple{Any,AbstractArray{T,1} where T}","page":"ForecastVerification","title":"ForecastVerification.brierscore","text":"BS = brierscore(y_true,y_prob::AbstractVector)\n\nCompute the Brier Score for a series of binary events ytrue, forecasted with a probability `yprob`\n\nBS = frac1Nsum_t=1^N(f_t - o_t)^2\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#ForecastVerification.brierscoredecom-Tuple{Any,AbstractArray{T,1} where T}","page":"ForecastVerification","title":"ForecastVerification.brierscoredecom","text":"BS,REL,RES,UNC = brierscoredecom(y_true,y_prob::AbstractVector)\n\nThe Brier score can be decomposed into 3 additive components: Uncertainty, Reliability, and Resolution. (Murphy 1973)>\n\nBS = REL - RES + UNC\n\nREL=frac1N sum_k=1^Kn_k(mathbff_k - mathbfbaro_mathbfk)^2\n\nRES = frac1Nsumlimits _k=1^Kn_k(mathbfbaro_k-barmathbfo)^2\n\nUNC = mathbfbaroleft(1-mathbfbaroright)\n\nWith N being the total number of forecasts issued, K the number of unique forecasts issued, mathbfbaro=sum_t=1^Nmathbfo_tN the observed climatological base rate for the event to occur, n_k the number of forecasts with the same probability category and mathbfoverlineo_mathbfk the observed frequency, given forecasts of probability mathbff_k.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#ForecastVerification.crms-Tuple{Any,Any}","page":"ForecastVerification","title":"ForecastVerification.crms","text":"crms(x,y)\n\nCentred root mean square difference between x and y\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#ForecastVerification.rms-Tuple{Any,Any}","page":"ForecastVerification","title":"ForecastVerification.rms","text":"rms(x,y)\n\nRoot mean square difference between x and y\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"}]
